metadata.name: Tiger or big cat
metadata.description:
This is the first job I have had the opportunity to work on this platform. I'm so glad I got the chance.
This work will be one of the 12 Zodiacs collection.
By this work of mine will be in the year of the tiger zodiac. Which I want to convey the cuteness of a tiger that sometimes I think it's like a cat, just that it's more frightening.
